.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, grey, amber, brown, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: american, chinese, french, polish, thai
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-fanta, mirinda, cola, fanta, lemonade
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: lilacmaster, game, vegafina, montecristo, alhambra
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, pony, hamster, guinea-pig
1. the american is the person who likes amber
2. the swedish is the owner of the pony
3. the chinese is the person drinking fanta
4. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes brown
5. the person who likes grey is the person drinking mirinda
6. the vegafina-smoker is the owner of the turtle
7. the person who likes blood-red is the game-smoker
8. the person drinking cola is in the middle
9. the polish is on the far left
10. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog
11. the owner of the guinea-pigs is on the left or right of the game-smoker
12. the lilacmaster-smoker is the person drinking iced-fanta
13. the french is the montecristo-smoker
14. the polish is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac
15. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    blood-red	|     lilac	|      amber	|     grey	|     brown	|
| Nationality	|   polish	|    chinese	|    american	|    french	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     hedgehog	|    guinea-pig	|     turtle	|     hamster	|      pony	|
| Beverage	|    lemonade	|     fanta	|     cola	|    mirinda	|      iced-fanta	|
| Cigar		|   game	|    alhambra	|  vegafina	|    montecristo	|   lilacmaster	|
